Build a Corporate Guest House Management System with two login portals — Super Admin and Guest House Manager. React + Tailwind CSS. Mock all data locally. No backend needed. Use a clean professional design.

---

## CORE CONCEPT

The manager is the human operator. There is no guest portal, no self-booking, no automation. The manager handles all communication with guests outside the system (phone, WhatsApp, email). The system is a tool the manager uses to record decisions, manage rooms, and generate reports.

When a booking is confirmed by admin, the system sends a confirmation email to the guest via SMTP (mocked in UI as a "Send Email" toast). Admin can assign a manager to multiple guest houses. Manager sees all assigned guest houses and can switch between them.

