## FINAL VALIDATION RULES (New Booking)

- All guest names + phones required
- At least 1 room selected
- No room conflict (check against existing confirmed/checked_in/pending bookings)
- All guests must be assigned a room (no unassigned guest)
- Check-out must be after check-in
- If pickup enabled: location + date + time required
- If drop enabled: location + date + time required
- Disable "Submit for Approval" button until all validations pass
- Show inline error messages per field, not just a single alert
